description:
By reason of our experiences with the material titanium we have become an internationally renowned partner in deep sea research.
In particular our titanium pressure housings, seamless and pressure tested up to 6000 m with guarantee, convince with their excellent quality at a reasonable price.
We test each tube at full pressure in our pressure chamber and accompany it with the certificate upon delivery.
Dependent on their use our titanium tubes are equipped with/without covers, connectors or plugs, threads, camera windows, grips ...
We manufacture according to your specific requirements!
